name: #6 Mountaindrone
description: Let the mountains take you for a walk. Follow their guidance, feel the space they create. Around you, inside your head. Working on your mind. In a very good way. The music was inspired on the picture, composed while I was there. The visuals were inspired on the music, overdubbed on the picture. They are dynamic clojure(quil) patches, live coded in conjunction with live patched modular music.
